content: 'A student poster session will be held with the reception on the Sunday before the conference (March 6). The student poster session is an excellent venue for graduate and undergraduate students to present and discuss their ongoing research work. The poster session features informal one-on-one interactions between presenters and other conference participants. The goal of the poster session is to help students obtain early feedback on their research projects and establish contacts with other researchers with similar interests.
